name: maps_ts
description: # Setup 1. First of all you need generate a Google dev project.     - Create new project or if you want use exciting one.     - In library we should find maps JavaScript api.     - console: https://console.developers.google.com/ 2. Enable google maps support inside the project 3. Generate api key 4. Add google maps script in the project. ```     <script src="https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/js?key=yout api key on step 3"></script> ```
